queries_executed.name: All_Generator_Nodes
queries_executed.query:
MATCH (g:Generator)
                RETURN 
                    g.name as name,
                    g.epa_id as epa_id,
                    g.address as address,
                    g.city as city,
                    g.state as state,
                    g.zip_code as zip_code,
                    g.phone as phone,
                    g.contact_person as contact_person,
                    properties(g) as all_properties
                ORDER BY g.name
